oth Judas and Silas, who were also prophets themselves, encouraged the brothers and sisters and strengthened them with a long message. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 14:22","book":"Act","chapter":14,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:1","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 14:22","book":"Act","chapter":14,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 15:1","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:15:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After spending some time there, they were sent back in peace "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 5:34","book":"Mrk","chapter":5,"verse":34,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:36","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":36,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:11","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:31","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":31,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" by the brothers and sisters to those who had sent them. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read the brothers to the apostles"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add v. 34: But Silas decided to stay there."},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 5:34","book":"Mrk","chapter":5,"verse":34},{"label":"Ac 16:36","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":36},{"label":"1Co 16:11","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":11},{"label":"Heb 11:31","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":31}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read the brothers to the apostles"},{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss add v. 34: But Silas decided to stay there."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Act:15:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But Paul and Barnabas, along with many others, remained in Antioch, teaching and proclaiming the word of the Lord. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:4","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:1","book":"Act"